                  basic command
                  1. to create project     -  ng new project name  //  
                  2. to run                -  ng serve --open
                  3. to create component   -  ng g c component name
                  3. to create service     -  ng g s component name
                 



                  Basic Concepts

                  1. component - to create { html,css,ts file}


                  3. Data Binding - data sharing b/w html and ts

                3.1  one way binding

                   3.1.1 component to view
                      
  ***                3.1.1.1 String Interpolation: syntax- {{variable-name}} 
                     3.1.1.2 Property Binding: [attribute]="variable-name"

                  3.1.2 view to component
                    
                     3.1.2.1 Event Binding-(event)="function-call()"

                     3.1.2.2 Event Binding using $event- (event)="function-call($event)"

                     3.1.2.3 Template Refrencing variable - syntax: #variable-name


               3.2   Two way binding-

                 3.2 Using ngModel - Import Formsmodule in AppModule
                     
                     syntax: [(ngModel)]="variable-name"

                 4. To Setup path for a component :

                     syntax: {path:'',component:componentClassName}    

                  5. Dependency Injection - to share data between classes

                  6. Angular Services  -  for redundant data

                  7. ngSubmit      -     to submit entire form   syntax: (ngsubmit)="function-call

                  8. Angular Forms

                    8.1 Template Driven Forms    - first design html

                    8.2 Model Driven Forms       -first create model in ts
                        
                        8.2.1 Reactive Forms  -  Add Validation : Import ReactiveFormsModule
                                 - form group -FormBuilder dependency Inject, form array form control